40static const int AI01_GTIN_SIZE = 40;
41
42static void
43AI01AppendCheckDigit(std::string& buffer, int currentPos)
44{
45 int checkDigit = 0;
46 for (int i = 0; i < 13; i++) {
47 int digit = buffer[i + currentPos] - '0';
48 checkDigit += (i & 0x01) == 0 ? 3 * digit : digit;
49 }
50
51 checkDigit = 10 - (checkDigit % 10);
52 if (checkDigit == 10) {
53 checkDigit = 0;
54 }
55 buffer.append(std::to_string(checkDigit));
56}
57
58static void
59AI01EncodeCompressedGtinWithoutAI(std::string& buffer, const BitArray& bits, int currentPos, int initialBufferPosition)
60{
61 for (int i = 0; i < 4; ++i) {
62 int currentBlock = GenericAppIdDecoder::ExtractNumeric(bits, currentPos + 10 * i, 10);
63 if (currentBlock / 100 == 0) {
64 buffer.push_back('0');
65 }
66 if (currentBlock / 10 == 0) {
67 buffer.push_back('0');
68 }
69 buffer.append(std::to_string(currentBlock));
70 }
71 AI01AppendCheckDigit(buffer, initialBufferPosition);
72}
73
74static void
75AI01EncodeCompressedGtin(std::string& buffer, const BitArray& bits, int currentPos)
76{
77 buffer.append("(01)");
78 int initialPosition = Size(buffer);
79 buffer.push_back('9');
80 AI01EncodeCompressedGtinWithoutAI(buffer, bits, currentPos, initialPosition);
81}
82
83using AddWeightCodeFunc = const std::function<void(std::string&, int)>;
84using CheckWeightFunc = const std::function<int (int)>;
85
86static void AI01EncodeCompressedWeight(std::string& buffer, const BitArray& bits, int currentPos, int weightSize,
87 const AddWeightCodeFunc& addWeightCode, const CheckWeightFunc& checkWeight)
88{
89 int originalWeightNumeric = GenericAppIdDecoder::ExtractNumeric(bits, currentPos, weightSize);
90 addWeightCode(buffer, originalWeightNumeric);
91
92 int weightNumeric = checkWeight(originalWeightNumeric);
93
94 int currentDivisor = 100000;
95 for (int i = 0; i < 5; ++i) {
96 if (weightNumeric / currentDivisor == 0) {
97 buffer.push_back('0');
98 }
99 currentDivisor /= 10;
100 }
101 buffer.append(std::to_string(weightNumeric));
102}

104/**
105* @author Pablo Ordu√±a, University of Deusto (pablo.orduna@deusto.es)
106* @author Eduardo Castillejo, University of Deusto (eduardo.castillejo@deusto.es)
107*/
108static std::string
109DecodeAI01AndOtherAIs(const BitArray& bits)
110{
111 static const int HEADER_SIZE = 1 + 1 + 2; //first bit encodes the linkage flag,
112 //the second one is the encodation method, and the other two are for the variable length
113 std::string buffer;
114 buffer.append("(01)");
115 int initialGtinPosition = Size(buffer);
116 int firstGtinDigit = GenericAppIdDecoder::ExtractNumeric(bits, HEADER_SIZE, 4);
117 buffer.append(std::to_string(firstGtinDigit));
118
119 AI01EncodeCompressedGtinWithoutAI(buffer, bits, HEADER_SIZE + 4, initialGtinPosition);
120 if (StatusIsOK(GenericAppIdDecoder::DecodeAllCodes(bits, HEADER_SIZE + 44, buffer))) {
121 return buffer;
122 }
123 return std::string();
124}
125
126static std::string
127DecodeAnyAI(const BitArray& bits)
128{
129 static const int HEADER_SIZE = 2 + 1 + 2;
130 std::string buffer;
131 if (StatusIsOK(GenericAppIdDecoder::DecodeAllCodes(bits, HEADER_SIZE, buffer))) {
132 return buffer;
133 }
134 return std::string();
135}
136
137static std::string
138DecodeAI013103(const BitArray& bits)
139{
140 static const int HEADER_SIZE = 4 + 1;
141 static const int WEIGHT_SIZE = 15;
142
143 if (bits.size() != HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE + WEIGHT_SIZE) {
144 return std::string();
145 }
146
147 std::string buffer;
148 AI01EncodeCompressedGtin(buffer, bits, HEADER_SIZE);
149 AI01EncodeCompressedWeight(buffer, bits, HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE, WEIGHT_SIZE,
150 // addWeightCode
151 [](std::string& buf, int) { buf.append("(3103)"); },
152 // checkWeight
153 [](int weight) { return weight; });
154
155 return buffer;
156}
157
158static std::string
159DecodeAI01320x(const BitArray& bits)
160{
161 static const int HEADER_SIZE = 4 + 1;
162 static const int WEIGHT_SIZE = 15;
163
164 if (bits.size() != HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE + WEIGHT_SIZE) {
165 return std::string();
166 }
167
168 std::string buffer;
169 AI01EncodeCompressedGtin(buffer, bits, HEADER_SIZE);
170 AI01EncodeCompressedWeight(buffer, bits, HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE, WEIGHT_SIZE,
171 // addWeightCode
172 [](std::string& buf, int weight) { buf.append(weight < 10000 ? "(3202)" : "(3203)"); },
173 // checkWeight
174 [](int weight) { return weight < 10000 ? weight : weight - 10000; });
175
176 return buffer;
177}
178
179static std::string
180DecodeAI01392x(const BitArray& bits)
181{
182 static const int HEADER_SIZE = 5 + 1 + 2;
183 static const int LAST_DIGIT_SIZE = 2;
184
185 if (bits.size() < HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE) {
186 return std::string();
187 }
188
189 std::string buffer;
190 AI01EncodeCompressedGtin(buffer, bits, HEADER_SIZE);
191
192 int lastAIdigit = GenericAppIdDecoder::ExtractNumeric(bits, HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE, LAST_DIGIT_SIZE);
193 buffer.append("(392");
194 buffer.append(std::to_string(lastAIdigit));
195 buffer.push_back(')');
196
197 if (StatusIsOK(GenericAppIdDecoder::DecodeGeneralPurposeField(bits, HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE + LAST_DIGIT_SIZE, buffer))) {
198 return buffer;
199 }
200 return std::string();
201}
202
203static std::string
204DecodeAI01393x(const BitArray& bits)
205{
206 static const int HEADER_SIZE = 5 + 1 + 2;
207 static const int LAST_DIGIT_SIZE = 2;
208 static const int FIRST_THREE_DIGITS_SIZE = 10;
209
210 if (bits.size() < HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE) {
211 return std::string();
212 }
213
214 std::string buffer;
215 AI01EncodeCompressedGtin(buffer, bits, HEADER_SIZE);
216
217 int lastAIdigit = GenericAppIdDecoder::ExtractNumeric(bits, HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE, LAST_DIGIT_SIZE);
218
219 buffer.append("(393");
220 buffer.append(std::to_string(lastAIdigit));
221 buffer.push_back(')');
222
223 int firstThreeDigits = GenericAppIdDecoder::ExtractNumeric(bits, HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE + LAST_DIGIT_SIZE, FIRST_THREE_DIGITS_SIZE);
224 if (firstThreeDigits / 100 == 0) {
225 buffer.push_back('0');
226 }
227 if (firstThreeDigits / 10 == 0) {
228 buffer.push_back('0');
229 }
230 buffer.append(std::to_string(firstThreeDigits));
231
232 if (StatusIsOK(GenericAppIdDecoder::DecodeGeneralPurposeField(bits, HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE + LAST_DIGIT_SIZE + FIRST_THREE_DIGITS_SIZE, buffer))) {
233 return buffer;
234 }
235 return std::string();
236}
237
238static std::string
239DecodeAI013x0x1x(const BitArray& bits, const char* firstAIdigits, const char* dateCode)
240{
241 static const int HEADER_SIZE = 7 + 1;
242 static const int WEIGHT_SIZE = 20;
243 static const int DATE_SIZE = 16;
244
245 if (bits.size() != HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE + WEIGHT_SIZE + DATE_SIZE) {
246 return std::string();
247 }
248
249 std::string buffer;
250 AI01EncodeCompressedGtin(buffer, bits, HEADER_SIZE);
251 AI01EncodeCompressedWeight(buffer, bits, HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE, WEIGHT_SIZE,
252 // addWeightCode
253 [firstAIdigits](std::string& buf, int weight) {
254 buf.push_back('(');
255 buf.append(firstAIdigits);
256 buf.append(std::to_string(weight / 100000));
257 buf.push_back(')');
258 },
259 // checkWeight
260 [](int weight) {
261 return weight % 100000;
262 });
263
264 // encode compressed date
265 int numericDate = GenericAppIdDecoder::ExtractNumeric(bits, HEADER_SIZE + AI01_GTIN_SIZE + WEIGHT_SIZE, DATE_SIZE);
266 if (numericDate != 38400) {
267 buffer.push_back('(');
268 buffer.append(dateCode);
269 buffer.push_back(')');
270
271 int day = numericDate % 32;
272 numericDate /= 32;
273 int month = numericDate % 12 + 1;
274 numericDate /= 12;
275 int year = numericDate;
276
277 if (year / 10 == 0) {
278 buffer.push_back('0');
279 }
280 buffer.append(std::to_string(year));
281 if (month / 10 == 0) {
282 buffer.push_back('0');
283 }
284 buffer.append(std::to_string(month));
285 if (day / 10 == 0) {
286 buffer.push_back('0');
287 }
288 buffer.append(std::to_string(day));
289 }
290
291 return buffer;
292}
293
294std::string
295ExpandedBinaryDecoder::Decode(const BitArray& bits)
296{
297 if (bits.get(1)) {
298 return DecodeAI01AndOtherAIs(bits);
299 }
300 if (!bits.get(2)) {
301 return DecodeAnyAI(bits);
302 }
303
304 int fourBitEncodationMethod = GenericAppIdDecoder::ExtractNumeric(bits, 1, 4);
305
306 switch (fourBitEncodationMethod) {
307 case 4: return DecodeAI013103(bits);
308 case 5: return DecodeAI01320x(bits);
309 }
310
311 int fiveBitEncodationMethod = GenericAppIdDecoder::ExtractNumeric(bits, 1, 5);
312 switch (fiveBitEncodationMethod) {
313 case 12: return DecodeAI01392x(bits);
314 case 13: return DecodeAI01393x(bits);
315 }
316
317 int sevenBitEncodationMethod = GenericAppIdDecoder::ExtractNumeric(bits, 1, 7);
318 switch (sevenBitEncodationMethod) {
319 case 56: return DecodeAI013x0x1x(bits, "310", "11");
320 case 57: return DecodeAI013x0x1x(bits, "320", "11");
321 case 58: return DecodeAI013x0x1x(bits, "310", "13");
322 case 59: return DecodeAI013x0x1x(bits, "320", "13");
323 case 60: return DecodeAI013x0x1x(bits, "310", "15");
324 case 61: return DecodeAI013x0x1x(bits, "320", "15");
325 case 62: return DecodeAI013x0x1x(bits, "310", "17");
326 case 63: return DecodeAI013x0x1x(bits, "320", "17");
327 }
328
329 return std::string();
330 //throw new IllegalStateException("unknown decoder: " + information);
331}
